# To Compile NGINX+ images

Step 1
======
cd to nginx-plus-ctrl-agent

Step 2
======
Identify the following parameter before hand
- CTRL_HOST ==> NGINX Controller FQDN
- API_KEY ==> NGINX Controller API_KEY
- Identify your private repository.

Example
Build
=====
docker build --no-cache --build-arg API_KEY=540286ae9ad5752ae7d7ca2d8ac527f8 --build-arg CTRL_HOST=nginx-ctrl.foobz.com.au  -t reg.foobz.com.au/foobz/nginx-plus-ctrl-agent:slim .


Push to private repository
==========================
docker push reg.foobz.com.au/foobz/nginx-plus-ctrl-agent:slim


